content.query:
SELECT top 100
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY TransactionId asc) as RentalSK,
    [TransactionId]
    ,[CustomerId]
    ,[MovieId]
    ,[RentalDate]
    ,[RentalCost]
    ,[LateFee]
    ,[RewindFlag]
    ,[CreatedDate]
    ,[UpdatedDate]
    ,[DataSourceId]
FROM dbo.Rentals
where DataSourceId = 2
